descriptionHtml:
Al Dar Exchange is one of the leading names in the Qatar remittance market and a pioneer in the industry of Qatar Money exchange business. We operated in QATAR as part of remittance market more than a decade.
ALDAR APP
 Send Account Transfer or Cash Pick up 24/7.

 Generate the receipt of the transaction at any time.
 Easily Contact to Customer Service for queries.

Kindly visit www.aldarexchange.com for more information.
